<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | FlavourFusion</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&family=Source+Code+Pro:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f5 0%, #ffe9e9 100%);
            color: #2d3436;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e74c3c, #ff7675);
        }
        
        .error-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .error-image {
            width: 280px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(0);
            }
            25% {
                transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(-5deg);
            }
            75% {
                transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(5deg);
            }
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #ff7675;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #2d3436;
            margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #636e72;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .url {
            background: #fff8f8;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            word-break: break-all;
            border: 2px dashed #ffcdd2;
            display: inline-block;
            max-width: 100%;
        }
        
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e74c3c, #ff7675);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
        }
        
        .home-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff7675, #e74c3c);
        }
        
        .emoji {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 0 0.3rem;
            animation: wave 2.5s infinite;
            display: inline-block;
            transform-origin: 70% 70%;
        }
        
        @keyframes wave {
            0%,
            100% {
                transform: rotate(0);
            }
            20%,
            60% {
                transform: rotate(-25deg);
            }
            40%,
            80% {
                transform: rotate(25deg);
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 2rem;
                border-radius: 20px;
            }
            .error-image {
                width: 200px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }
            .message {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
            .error-image {
                width: 160px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }
            .home-button {
                padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
        
        .pattern-box {
            background: #2d3436;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            font-family: 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
            text-align: left;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .box-title {
            position: absolute;
            top: -12px;
            left: 20px;
            background: #e74c3c;
            padding: 2px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .path-match {
            color: #00b894;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .analysis {
            color: #81ecec;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #636e72;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            background: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
            padding: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #ff7675;
        }
        
        @keyframes blink {
            0%,
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
        }
        
        .cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 15px;
            background: #ff7675;
            margin-left: 5px;
            animation: blink 1s infinite;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .pattern-box {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                padding: 1.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-content">
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2674/2674505.png" alt="404 Error" class="error-image">
            <h1>404</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Invalid Path <span class="emoji">üîç</span></div>
            <p class="message">
                The requested URL doesn't exist in our recipe collection.
            </p>

            <div class="pattern-box">
                <span class="box-title">Path Analysis</span>
                <div class="path-match">
                    Requested Path: <span class="highlight"><%= url %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="analysis">
                    # System Analysis:<br> - Path validation failed<br> - No matching route found<br> - Suggestion: Verify URL or return to homepage
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/" class="home-button">Back to Homepage</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>